Reflection - Module14 BREAD Calculations

In this assignment, I implemented complete BREAD functionality for calculations using FastAPI. I created endpoints for browse, read, add, edit, and delete operations. I also worked with SQLite database models and user authentication features.

One challenge I faced was handling authorization inside Swagger UI. I learned how API authentication works and how endpoints are protected for users. Another challenge was debugging indentation and schema issues, which helped me improve problem-solving skills.

I also learned how to use Docker to containerize the application and push the image to Docker Hub. Updating the README and organizing project files helped me understand professional project structure.

Overall, this assignment improved my backend development, debugging, API testing, and deployment skills.
